snippet.title: Drifting  Weight of Feathers Gameplay (PC Game)
snippet.description: A third-person shooter action game. Each encounter in the game challenges the player to develop a situational awareness in 3D space, which includes constantly prioritizing your target whilst observing the surroundings to find out the key to advance to the next stage
